      "desc": "The Byzantine evolution of the trireme \u2014 larger, carrying a siphon for Greek fire, and crewed by professional marines of the Eastern Roman navy. She fights with fire rather than the ram, and the psychological impact of a ship that sprays liquid flame is worth more than any weapon system.",
